    <node id="SERVICE_PERIOD">
      <data key="d0">ATTRIBUTE</data>
      <data key="d1">The **SERVICE_PERIOD** entity represents the active billing period covered by an invoice, formatted as a date range string in `YYYY-MM-DD to YYYY-MM-DD` (e.g., `2023-01-01 to 2023-01-31`). This field is parsed to extract discrete service start and end dates, enabling temporal filtering and analytical operations such as period-based aggregation or trend analysis. The standardized format ensures consistency for downstream processes that rely on precise date boundaries derived from the invoice data.</data>
